(330, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', '', '', 'home', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '<h1>Company Scientific and Production Association SPECSINTEZ. Stability, reliability, striving for the best!</h1>\r\n<p>Our company is one of the leading manufacturers of professional detergents and disinfectants.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup><col /> <col /> <col /> <col /> <col /> </colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center><strong>We develop</strong></center></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td><center><strong>We produce</strong></center></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td><center><strong>We impliment</strong></center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p align="justify">Specialists of scientific lab "SPA Specsintez" have created a wide range of modern chemical products of superior quality. They are based on own innovative technologies designed for professional cleaning and disinfection</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p align="justify">The scope of our activities is production of detergents and disinfectants. We are proud of our own research and manufactural base, that uses advanced technology, excellent quality raw materials and modern equipment, that allows to produce high quality and competitive products to guarantee cleanliness and disinfection.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p align="justify">Selling of industrial and household chemicals, disinfectants and means of personal protection is a key stage of our manufacture. Detergents from the manufacturer is a guarantee of purchasing high quality products at the optimal prices!</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong><big><br />Professional chemistry manufacturer</big></strong></span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"> Company SPA Specsintez specialize on development and manufacturing of means for different sectors of economy. Our products are widely demanded and successfully used in different scopes and spheres of consumption:</span></p>\r\n<ul class="list3">\r\n<li>medical institutions of healthcare and social security</li>\r\n<li>objects of railway transport and subway</li>\r\n<li>food industry</li>\r\n<li>public catering institutions</li>\r\n<li>trade, communal facilities</li>\r\n<li>hospitality industry</li>\r\n<li>cleaning</li>\r\n<li>veterinary</li>\r\n<li>mechanical engineering and metallurgy</li>\r\n<li>labor safety</li>\r\n<li>maintenance of heat exchange equipment</li>\r\n<li>beauty salons and SPA</li>\r\n<li>schools and kindergartens</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"></p>\r\n<p align="justify">Acting quickly and flexibly, anticipating the needs of our customers, we do our best to satisfy their queries and find solutions of unusual problems.</p><p></p>\r\n<p align="justify">Any serious and responsible task, whether it is disinfection of a restaurant, washing railcars, degreasing items, cleaning of swimming pools, disinfection and sterilization of medical tools, hand hygiene of staff, is successfully exercised with usage our products.</p><p></p>\r\n<p align="justify">All employees are single team, in which competence, responsibility, reliability are highly appreciated.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Main idea of our company is expressed in intention to fully meet our clients needs in efficient detergents, in continuous improvement, in implementation of future technologies of the domestic and global chemistry in our developments. Product quality and service level form basic foundation, on which our partnerships with consumers is built. Cleanliness and hygiene is the basis of human health and life. Our disinfectants and cosmetic products will provide necessary sanitary-epidemiological regime, will make safe the production of your enterprise and technological process for your employees.</p><p></p>\r\n<p align="justify">Modern cleaning is both washing and disinfection. Manufacturer of disinfectants and liquid soaps "SPA Specsintez" produces a wide range of products to ensure infectious security. Our production is featured by high efficiency, low toxicity, activity of small concentrations and short exposure terms, wide spectrum of action, combination of means with a cleaning and disinfectant properties, safety for personnel and the objects being processed, storage stability and ease of transportation.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h4>Our company benefits:</h4>\r\n<ul class="list3">\r\n<li>expertise</li>\r\n<li>own laboratory base for development and manufacturing of disinfectors of wide range</li>\r\n<li>strict control of raw materials and finished products</li>\r\n<li>quality and stability</li>\r\n<li>balance of high quality and affordable price</li>\r\n<li>detergent wholesale from manufacturer is a convenient and beneficial decision</li>\r\n<li>individual approach to every business associate</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, 7, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1386583475, 94, 1488416471, 0, 0, 0, 1386588420, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'en', 1, 'home', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
