(1136, 'document', 'text/html', 'Triosept-Mix', '', '', 'triosept-mix', '', 1, 0, 0, 1228, 0, 'Disinfectant with the expressed washing effect. Concentrate', '<h4>Low-toxiferous agent with the expressed washing effect.<br />It is awarded awards"Dezreesrt optima award-2008" for an optimum ratio of consumer characteristics, scientifically reasonable concentration of DV in working solutions, profitability, polyfunctionality.</h4>\r\n<ul style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Agent of wide scope of application for work in LPU of any profile</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>It is recommended for children''s hospitals and out-patient departments, neonatology units (for disinfection of couveuses), obstetric establishments</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Agent low-toxiferous, 4-5 class of low-dangerous substances</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Doesn''t possess sensitizing action</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Has the expressed washing properties</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Doesn''t demand washing off from a povernost after processing</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Economically for disinfection and ware washing, it is easily washed away from a surface</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Doesn''t contain fragrances, has no smell</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>It is used for:</strong></h4>\r\n<ul style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Disinfection of surfaces on premises, furnishings, surfaces of apparatuses (mechanisms) and devises, sanitary and technical facilities, cleaning facilities, health products, dishes, laboratory dishes, toys, personal hygiene items in prevention and treatment clinics, , including departments of neonatology, childrens and gynecological departments, communal facilities (hairdressing salons, beauty salons, baths, industrial markets, public toilets), catering and food trade establishments, childcare facilities when carrying out current, final and preventive disinfection;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Disinfection of incubators in departments of neonatology</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Carrying out general orders in prevention and treatment clinics (including sanatoriums, health care centers, guest houses, rest homes), communal facilities, catering and food trade establishments, childcare facilities</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Disinfection of sanitary transport and transport for food</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Before sterilization (or final  before high level disinfection of endoscopes) cleaning and disinfection, combined with pre- sterilization cleaning medical products, including surgical, dental instruments, rigid and flexible endoscopes and instruments to them by manual and mechanized (with the use of ultrasound) methods in prevention and treatment clinics</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Disinfection and cleaning of dental preparations made of metals, ceramics, plastics and another materials, dental reprints made of alginates, silicon, polymorphic resin (tar), articulates, saliva ejector systems, spittoon in dental clinics</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="font-size: 14px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside;">\r\n<p>Disinfection of medical waste (including disposable medical products) before utilization</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, 6, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1389862728, 1, 1389869641, 0, 0, 0, 1386049860, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'modDocument', 'en', 1, 'produkcziyaen/other/triosept-mix', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
