display/ADDON/Babel" target="_blank">http://rtfm.modx.com/display/ADDON/Babel</a>. You may have a look at our tutorial for <a href="http://www.class-zec.com/en/blog/2011/multilingual-websites-with-modx-and-babel.html">setting up your multilingual website with MODx and Babel</a>.</p>\n<p>Feel free to suggest ideas/improvements/bugs on GitHub:<a href="https://github.com/mikrobi/babel/issues" target="_blank"> https://github.com/mikrobi/babel/issues</a></p>\n<p>New in 2.2.5-pl</p><ul><li>Extended list of languages in translation files and added Romanian translation.</li><li>Issue #31: Maked babel buttons in manager position fixed and changed look accordingly.</li></ul><p>New in 2.2.4-pl</p><ul><li>Fixed issue #25: Unchecked "checkbox" TVs are now synchronized correctly.\n</li><li>Issue #22: Added showCurrent parameter to BabelLinks snippet.</li></ul><p>New in 2.2.3-rc1</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Issue #18: Added ''id'' placeholder for BabelLink chunk which is used by the BabelLinks snippet.</li>\n<li>Fixed issue #21: Manager redirect causes error in Google Chrome browser.</li>\n</ul>";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:12;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:12:"instructions";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:342:"<p>Install via package management and set configuration parameters in the setup dialog according to your needs.</p>\n<p>If you''re having problems take a look at this <a href="http://www.class-zec.com/en/blog/2011/multilingual-websites-with-modx-and-babel.html">tutorial describing the setup of a multilingual site using MODx and Babel</a>.</p>";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:13;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"changelog";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:727:"<p>Babel 2.2.5-pl</p>\n<ul><li>Extended list of languages in translation files and added Romanian translation.</li><li>Issue #31: Maked babel buttons in manager position fixed and changed look accordingly.</li></ul>\n<p>Babel 2.2.4-pl</p><ul><li>Fixed issue #25: Unchecked "checkbox" TVs are now synchronized correctly.</li><li>Issue #22: Added showCurrent parameter to BabelLinks snippet.</li></ul>Babel 2.2.3-rc1<ul><li>Issue #18: Added ''id'' placeholder for BabelLink chunk which is used by the BabelLinks snippet.</li><li>Fixed issue #21: Manager redirect causes error in Google Chrome browser.</li></ul>Babel 2.2.2-rc2<ul><li>Fixed bug: Initial synchronization of TV values when setting a link manually didn''t work.</li></ul>";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:14;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"createdon";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:23:"2011-12-11 12:58:00 UTC";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:15;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:10:"created_by";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:7:"mikrobi";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:16;a:3:{s:4:"name";s:8:"editedon";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:17;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:10:"releasedon";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:23:"2011-12-11 12:58:00 UTC";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:18;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"downloads";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:5:"11127";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:19;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:8:"approved";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:4:"true";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:20;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:7:"audited";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:5:"false";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:21;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:8:"featured";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:5:"false";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:22;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:10:"deprecated";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:5:"false";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:23;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:7:"license";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:5:"GPLv2";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:24;a:3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"smf_url";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:25;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:4:"name";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:5:"Babel";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:26;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:10:"repository";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:24:"4d4c3fa6b2b0830da9000001";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:27;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:8:"supports";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:3:"2.0";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:28;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:10:"screenshot";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:70:"http://modx.s3.amazonaws.com/extras/4d